  "2374190": {
    "name": "Nikoderiko: The Magical World — Director’s Cut",
    "steam_appid": 2374190,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374190/extras/5a2332b5d0449c566f39e9a783ce85f4.poster.avif?t=1770807918\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374190/extras/5a2332b5d0449c566f39e9a783ce85f4.webm?t=1770807918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374190/extras/5a2332b5d0449c566f39e9a783ce85f4.mp4?t=1770807918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入《Nikoderiko:The Magical World》（导演剪辑版）的冒险，给平台游戏的一封情书！拯救《尼克德里克》中的魔法岛！畅玩这款迷人的平台冒险游戏，单人或在沙发上和朋友合作皆可，同时欣赏传奇作曲家 David Wise 的曲子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374190/extras/f028aec037546a15fbeccc7a5ad3dbcf.poster.avif?t=1770807918\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374190/extras/f028aec037546a15fbeccc7a5ad3dbcf.webm?t=1770807918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374190/extras/f028aec037546a15fbeccc7a5ad3dbcf.mp4?t=1770807918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>加入冒险！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>当一座魔法岛屿落入格林巴德男爵及其库布林军队的魔爪时，两只寻宝的猫鼬响应了召唤，开始了冒险。带着尼克和露娜穿越充满活力的 2.5D 世界，其中充满了平台狂欢、超大规模的首领战、矿车骑行、水下冒险，甚至经典的 3D 片段。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374190/extras/52331db4cfeb2832f5465a8db284a042.poster.avif?t=1770807918\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374190/extras/52331db4cfeb2832f5465a8db284a042.webm?t=1770807918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374190/extras/52331db4cfeb2832f5465a8db284a042.mp4?t=1770807918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>穿越奇幻的八个世界！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在穿越八个世界的丰富关卡时，考验你的平台技能。探索雪国的冰霜山峰、神秘的魔法树林和干涸之海的咸水深处——并留意沿途隐藏的秘密收藏品。无论你是经典平台游戏的粉丝，还是刚刚踏入征程，每个人都能在这里找到自己喜欢的元素！ </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374190/extras/116313434c2d65851ff05b951b2a9427.poster.avif?t=1770807918\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374190/extras/116313434c2d65851ff05b951b2a9427.webm?t=1770807918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374190/extras/116313434c2d65851ff05b951b2a9427.mp4?t=1770807918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>骑乘动物坐骑！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收集并召唤遍布世界各地的动物朋友！骑着它们前往新的地方，或使用它们的特殊攻击来对抗敌人。用野猪波瑞斯攻击敌人，骑上蟾蜍托德进行高空跳跃，骑上海马海尼斯驾驭海浪，或者使用迪诺来体验一把史前时代的感觉。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374190/extras/6ef68e77dd1d86d950875c2ef5dbb2d6.poster.avif?t=1770807918\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374190/extras/6ef68e77dd1d86d950875c2ef5dbb2d6.webm?t=1770807918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374190/extras/6ef68e77dd1d86d950875c2ef5dbb2d6.mp4?t=1770807918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挑战自我！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据你的技能水平定制游戏！年轻的粉丝和平台游戏新手可以从简单模式开始，而普通模式则提供一些可以轻松玩转的内容。困难模式和挑战修改器将会为真正的平台游戏专业玩家带来刺激。镜像关卡？这里有！被小气的十字准线追赶？这里也有！还有更多棘手的挑战等着测试你的平台勇气。你能胜任这个任务吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受美妙音乐！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个魔幻世界的音乐由传奇作曲家 David Wise 创作，他因在著名平台游戏中的经典作品而闻名。打开游戏、调高音量，让神奇的旋律带你回到平台游戏的黄金时代！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*我们的英雄和反派都学会了新的语言！在《NikoderikoThe Magical World》（导演剪辑版）中，体验法语、德语、西班牙语、日语、巴西葡萄牙语和简体中文的全套配音。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
